[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":315},["ShallowReactive",2],{"$W2mYtLpoab":3,"BJATIsuDhv":4},"# Pixiv Manager\n\nMade this tool coz I am too lazy to download each illustration after bookmarking them (especially on other devices).\n\nThen I added more functions to help me find images I want.\n\n## Screenshots\n\n![img.png](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/octo-kumo/pixiv-manager/master/github/images/img.png)\n![img.png](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/octo-kumo/pixiv-manager/master/github/images/img2.png)\n\n## Filter (Tristate)\n\n- R-18\n- AI\n- Landscape\n- Visible\n- Restricted\n- Bookmarked\n- Tags\n    - Contains all tag specified\n- Tools\n    - Uses all tools specified\n- Search bar\n    - Contains query\n\n## Sorting (Bidirectional + Multi-sorting)\n\n- ID\n- Views\n- Bookmarks\n- Bookmarks per View\n- Date\n- Sanity (How erotic it is)\n- Pixel\n- Pages\n- sRGB difference to chosen color\n- Hue difference to chosen color\n\n## Other functions\n\n- Bookmark toggle\n- Download\n- Drag & Drog / Copy (as file)\n- Open in Pixiv/Local\n- Follow toggle\n- Artist page\n- Recommend page\n- Feed page (+ ranking page)\n- Bookmark page\n- Advanced search page (+tags, bookmark count, autocomplete)\n\n## Problems\n\n- Amateur and naive optimizing\n    - Hundreds of megabytes of I/O.\n    - Memory usage at gigabyte scale.\n    - FPS barely above 60 on 1650ti.\n    - Rare but lag spikes exists.\n\n## Running it\n\nRequires your pixiv refresh token.\n\nRequires a custom fork of pixivj, maybe I will try to remove this dependency in the future.\n\n(Cloning this repository does not mean you can run it)\n",{"data":5,"body":8,"excerpt":-1,"toc":305},{"title":6,"description":7},"Pixiv Manager","Made this tool coz I am too lazy to download each illustration after bookmarking them (especially on other devices).",{"type":9,"children":10},"root",[11,19,24,29,36,49,55,129,135,188,194,247,253,284,290,295,300],{"type":12,"tag":13,"props":14,"children":16},"element","h1",{"id":15},"pixiv-man